item.description:
To set a setting, use dh!settings set &lt;parameter&gt; &lt;value&gt;
You can view modified settings by using dh!settings modified
For resetting a setting to its default value, use dh!settings reset &lt;parameter&gt;
   Parameter Type Default value Comment     announce_level_up bool True Toggle the level up/down announcements   bang_lag float 0.5 Time in seconds between a hunter&rsquo;s shot and what happens. This can be disabled by setting it to 0.
